title: Embraer E-Jets EPOP Performance Tool
description:
Embraer Portable Operational Package:

What is it?

EPOP is the official Embraer takeoff and landing performance calculation software. It's very similar to Boeing OPT or TOPCAT, but just for the Embraer E-Jets. 


System requirements:

32 bit Windows Operating System. This software works on both XP and Windows 7 but they must be 32 bit!

If you don't have a 32 bit OS you can easily get VMWare or Virtual Box and run a virtual PC with windows XP. 

I have more of this type of software that I might upload if there's an interest.


Any questions please ask,
